'''Puñal''' is a [[city]] in [[Santiago de los Caballeros Province|Santiago Province]]. Puñal became a rural section of the municipality of [[Santiago de los Caballeros]] in 1937, comprising the spots: Guayabal, Matanzas and Laguna Prieta. In February 2006 the rural section of Puñal was raised to the category of municipality. Puñal comprises the municipal districts Guayabal, Canabacoa, Arenoso, La Javilla and Matanzas.
